## 🔄 Bot ↔ Mini App Integration

### Flow: Bot Opens Mini App

```python
# Bot handler (Python)
@router.message(Command("stats"))
async def stats_command(message: Message):
    webapp_url = f"https://dealquest.app/dashboard?user={message.from_user.id}"
    
    await message.answer(
        "📊 View your full dashboard:",
        reply_markup=InlineKeyboardMarkup(inline_keyboard=[[
            InlineKeyboardButton(
                text="Open Dashboard",
                web_app=WebAppInfo(url=webapp_url)
            )
        ]])
    )
```

### Flow: Mini App Sends Data to Bot

```typescript
// Mini App (React)
import { useTelegram } from '@/hooks/useTelegram';

function ScenarioComplete({ score, xp }: Props) {
  const { sendData } = useTelegram();
  
  const handleComplete = () => {
    // Send data back to bot
    sendData(JSON.stringify({
      action: 'scenario_complete',
      score,
      xp,
      scenario_id: currentScenario.id
    }));
  };
  
  return (
    <MainButton 
      text="Complete & Return to Chat" 
      onClick={handleComplete} 
    />
  );
}
```

### Auth Flow

```
1. User opens Mini App from bot
2. Telegram passes initData (signed)
3. Mini App sends initData to InsForge
4. InsForge verifies signature
5. InsForge returns JWT
6. Mini App uses JWT for all API calls
```

